+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: sum(lineitem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * lineitem.L_DISCOUNT) AS REVENUE                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   Aggregate: groupBy=[[]], aggr=[[sum(lineitem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * lineitem.L_DISCOUNT)]]                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |     Projection: lineitem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, lineitem.L_DISCOUNT                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |         Filter: lineitem.L_SHIPDATE >= Date32("1994-01-01") AND lineitem.L_SHIPDATE < Date32("1995-01-01")                                                                                                                                           |
|               |           TableScan: lineitem projection=[L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L_DISCOUNT, L_SHIPDATE], full_filters=[lineitem.L_DISCOUNT >= Decimal128(Some(5),4,2), lineitem.L_DISCOUNT <= Decimal128(Some(7),4,2), lineitem.L_QUANTITY < Decimal128(Some(2400),12,2)] |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[sum(lineitem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * lineitem.L_DISCOUNT)@0 as REVENUE]                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |   AggregateExec: mode=Final, gby=[], aggr=[sum(lineitem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * lineitem.L_DISCOUNT)]                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |     CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[], aggr=[sum(lineitem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * lineitem.L_DISCOUNT)]                                                                                                                                                |
|               |         ProjectionExec: expr=[L_EXTENDEDPRICE@0 as L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L_DISCOUNT@1 as L_DISCOUNT]                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |             CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |               FilterExec: L_SHIPDATE@2 >= 1994-01-01 AND L_SHIPDATE@2 < 1995-01-01                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                 RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                   OracleExec sql=SELECT "L_EXTENDEDPRICE", "L_DISCOUNT", "L_SHIPDATE" FROM "TPCH_SF1"."LINEITEM" WHERE ("L_DISCOUNT" >= 0.05) AND ("L_DISCOUNT" <= 0.07) AND ("L_QUANTITY" < 24.00)                                                  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
